  This path resolves to a shared/ package that does NOT exist in jam-sandbox
  (it lives in the taskboard-supabase workspace). The component will fail to
  compile.

  AgentAvatar.vue uses these Profile fields:
    profile.actor_type    — 'agent' | string
    profile.agent_avatar_url
    profile.agent_name
    profile.avatar_url
    profile.full_name
    profile.email

steps:
  1. Remove the shared/types import.
  2. Declare a minimal local interface at the top of <script setup>:
       interface Profile {
         actor_type?: string
         agent_avatar_url?: string | null
         agent_name?: string | null
         avatar_url?: string | null
         full_name?: string | null
         email?: string | null
       }
  3. No other logic changes.

done:
